{"id":306858,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-四川西昌警察非法敛财，村民拍照被殴打/","date":"2013-08-01T14:33:27Z","modified":"2013-08-01T14:33:27Z","title":"维权网 | 四川西昌警察非法敛财，村民拍照被殴打（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员徐闯报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>，四川省西昌市西郊乡长安村一租房客摩托车被盗，当日，去辖区派出所报案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>宁远派出所未作任何调查，就通知房老板杨桂英去派出所交纳</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span>元罚金，并说：如不交罚金将行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据当地村民说：一名旁观者张桂花为取证，掏出手机准备拍照时，被女警察邓英上前抢走手机（至今未归还），随后邻居张桂花又从挎包里掏出手机准备继续拍，警察邓英发疯似的冲上来抢张桂花的手机，在场的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>个警察直接参与配合邓英抢走手机，邓英仰仗人多势众抓起啤酒易拉罐砸向张桂花，将张桂花的额头打出一个大口子，脸部打肿，当场流血不止，到医院缝合了三针。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警警察来到现场，既不对伤者施救，又不调查取证，袖手旁观看热闹。警察的此举引起当地市民的极大不满。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-x0iipKAlWPg/UfpO9VstSeI/AAAAAAAAmME/RKy71zSZz_U/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-x0iipKAlWPg/UfpO9VstSeI/AAAAAAAAmME/RKy71zSZz_U/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qiC2lcY-69Y/UfpO_inpDbI/AAAAAAAAmMM/azTIbeJZZxM/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"233\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qiC2lcY-69Y/UfpO_inpDbI/AAAAAAAAmMM/azTIbeJZZxM/s320/4.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75d